### Create order (valid)
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "items": [
    {"productId": "p1", "quantity": 2},
    {"productId": "p2", "quantity": 1}
  ],
  "totalPrice": 300,
  "status": "pending"
}

### List orders
GET http://localhost:3000/orders?page=1&limit=5

### Get order by id (replace)
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/000000000000000000000000

### Update order status (replace id)
PUT http://localhost:3000/orders/000000000000000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paid"
}

### Delete order (replace id)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/orders/000000000000000000000000

